Copper Ingot=Kupariharkko
Molten Copper. It is used to craft armor, tools, and blocks.=
Copper Material=Kuparimateriaali
Copper Nugget=
Copper nuggets are very small pieces of molten copper; the main purpose is to create copper ingots.=
